| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0806 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6048eb1a-a5e7-5b2c-b4eb-07135663b87d"
